241
00:21:27,517 --> 00:21:30,207
General Director Choi, even a fly has its anger.

242
00:21:30,207 --> 00:21:34,227
And a rat bites a cat when it's cornered.

243
00:21:34,227 --> 00:21:35,607
Chief Park.

244
00:21:35,607 --> 00:21:40,717
